      <title>越南在“烈火熔炉”反腐运动中罢免副总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/vietnam-ousts-deputy-pm-in-blazing-furnace-anti-graft-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南国会以违反反腐败规定为由，解除了又一名副总理的职务，继续了已故共产党总书记阮富仲领导的反腐败运动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/vietnam-ousts-deputy-pm-in-blazing-furnace-anti-graft-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>突尼斯领导人在十月投票前更换大部分内阁成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/tunisian-president-swaps-out-much-of-cabinet-before-october-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯总统更换了十几位政府部长，他称这是在十月份他很有可能获胜的选举之前打击腐败的“不可或缺的”举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/tunisian-president-swaps-out-much-of-cabinet-before-october-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪支持率在新民意调查中下滑，反对党领袖支持率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/modi-s-popularity-dips-in-new-poll-as-opposition-leader-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新调查显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪仍然是该国领导人最受欢迎的人选，尽管他的支持率稳步下降，而反对派的拉胡尔·甘地则支持这一结果，这与最近的选举结果基本一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/modi-s-popularity-dips-in-new-poll-as-opposition-leader-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:03:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾爆发抗议活动，警方瞄准杜特尔特牧师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/protests-erupt-in-philippines-as-police-target-duterte-s-pastor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，菲律宾南部城市达沃爆发暴力抗议活动，警方试图逮捕一名与前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特家族有联系的福音派传教士，这加深了该强大家族与总统费迪南德·马科斯之间的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/protests-erupt-in-philippines-as-police-target-duterte-s-pastor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相河野太郎呼吁在竞选自民党党魁时严守财政纪律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/japan-s-taro-kono-calls-for-fiscal-discipline-in-entering-ldp-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前外务兼防卫大臣河野太郎成为第三位竞选日本执政党自民党领袖的议员，他呼吁国家恢复财政纪律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/japan-s-taro-kono-calls-for-fiscal-discipline-in-entering-ldp-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 07:26:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体称，饱受战争蹂躏的苏丹大坝垮塌造成至少 60 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/dam-collapse-in-war-torn-sudan-kills-at-least-60-media-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，苏丹东部暴雨导致一座水坝垮塌，造成至少 60 人死亡，这是这个北非国家因长达一年多的内战而陷入饥荒的最新悲剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/dam-collapse-in-war-torn-sudan-kills-at-least-60-media-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈西娜退出后孟加拉国开始进行经济清理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/bangladesh-starts-economic-clean-up-after-hasina-s-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国将对前总理谢赫·哈西娜执政期间涉嫌夸大经济表现的数据异常进行调查，以根除过去 15 年大部分时间困扰这个南亚国家的腐败现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/bangladesh-starts-economic-clean-up-after-hasina-s-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:52:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
